### 1️⃣ Add a New Mood Entry
POST http://localhost:3000/api/moods
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "mood": "Happy",
  "notes": "Feeling great today!"
}

### 2️⃣ Delete a Mood Entry
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/moods/2

### 3️⃣ Get All Mood Entries for a Specific User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/moods/user/1

### 4️⃣ Get All Mood Entries (All Users)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/moods/all

### 5️⃣ Get Mood Entries by Date Range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/moods/user/1/date-range?startDate=2024-02-01&endDate=2024-02-20

### 6️⃣ Get Mood Statistics for a User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/moods/user/1/stats

### 7️⃣ Update a Mood Entry
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/moods/2
Content-Type: application/json

